RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: CYTMS_RATES_MASTER.BRANCH_CODE = CYTMS_RATES.BRANCH_CODE AND CYTMS_RATES_MASTER.CCY1 = CYTMS_RATES.CCY1 AND CYTMS_RATES_MASTER.CCY2 = CYTMS_RATES.CCY2

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select ccy1 , ccy2 , quotation , spread_defn , points_multiplier from cytms_ccy_pair_defn where auth_stat ='A' and record_stat = 'O' and through_ccy is null Order by ccy1

SELECT CCY_RATE_TYPE, CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC FROM CYTMS_RATE_TYPE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND ONCE_AUTH= 'Y' AND CCY_RATE_TYPE NOT IN ( SELECT RATE_TYPE FROM CYTMS_RATES WHERE CCY1 = ? AND CCY2 = ? AND BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH )
